### Transaction Rollback Module - HTTP Requests
### Port: 8083
### Rollback Ne Zaman Olur? Öğrenme Modülü

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8083
@contentType = application/json

### 1. RuntimeException → Rollback olur
### ✅ RuntimeException, Error → rollback (default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rollback/runtime-exception
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-001",
  "amount": 100.0
}

###

### 2. Checked Exception → Rollback olmaz (default)
### ❌ Checked Exception → rollback olmaz (default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rollback/checked-exception
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-002",
  "amount": 200.0
}

###

### 3. rollbackFor = Exception.class → Tüm exception'larda rollback
### ✅ rollbackFor ile tüm exception'larda rollback
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rollback/rollback-for-all
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-003",
  "amount": 300.0
}

###

### 4. noRollbackFor → Belirli exception'da rollback olmasın
### ✅ noRollbackFor ile belirli exception'da rollback olmaz
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rollback/no-rollback
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-004",
  "amount": 400.0
}

###

### 5. Başarılı işlem
### Normal başarılı transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rollback/success
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-005",
  "amount": 500.0
}

###


